{"hash":"f3d9fb9e6c8e2bbed6dbc844ed218f78af1ba203","data":{"metadata":{"siteName":"CSS Itu Mudah | e-book by Naufal Rabbani","bookTitle":"CSS Itu Mudah","author":{"name":"Naufal Rabbani","email":"bosnaufalemail@gmail.com"}},"allContent":{"totalCount":11,"edges":[{"node":{"title":"Perkenalan","path":"/chapter/perkenalan/","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Motivasi","anchor":"#motivasi"},{"depth":2,"value":"Daftar Isi","anchor":"#daftar-isi"},{"depth":2,"value":"Credits","anchor":"#credits"}]}},{"node":{"title":"Sekilas Tentang CSS","path":"/chapter/sekilas-tentang-css/","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Pengertian CSS","anchor":"#pengertian-css"},{"depth":2,"value":"Fungsi CSS","anchor":"#fungsi-css"},{"depth":2,"value":"Pentingnya CSS","anchor":"#pentingnya-css"}]}},{"node":{"title":"Hello World","path":"/chapter/hello-world/","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Persiapan","anchor":"#persiapan"},{"depth":2,"value":"Membuat File HTML","anchor":"#membuat-file-html"},{"depth":2,"value":"Buka File HTML Di Browser","anchor":"#buka-file-html-di-browser"},{"depth":2,"value":"Lah kok gini doang mas?","anchor":"#lah-kok-gini-doang-mas"}]}},{"node":{"title":"Basic Penulisan","path":"/chapter/basic-penulisan/","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Inline Styling","anchor":"#inline-styling"},{"depth":2,"value":"Style Tag","anchor":"#style-tag"},{"depth":2,"value":"External CSS File","anchor":"#external-css-file"}]}},{"node":{"title":"Bagian-bagian dari CSS","path":"/chapter/bagian-bagian-dari-css/","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Bagian-bagian dari CSS","anchor":"#bagian-bagian-dari-css"},{"depth":2,"value":"Selector","anchor":"#selector"},{"depth":2,"value":"Prioritas Aturan Pada CSS","anchor":"#prioritas-aturan-pada-css"},{"depth":2,"value":"Macam-Macam Selector","anchor":"#macam-macam-selector"},{"depth":2,"value":"Property","anchor":"#property"},{"depth":2,"value":"Value","anchor":"#value"}]}},{"node":{"title":"Konsep Box","path":"/chapter/konsep-box/","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Berkenalan Dengan ","anchor":"#berkenalan-dengan-div"},{"depth":2,"value":"Membentuk Paradigma","anchor":"#membentuk-paradigma"},{"depth":2,"value":"Mengenal Paddding","anchor":"#mengenal-paddding"},{"depth":2,"value":"Mengenal Margin","anchor":"#mengenal-margin"},{"depth":2,"value":"Mengenal Display Mode","anchor":"#mengenal-display-mode"}]}},{"node":{"title":"Advance Selector","path":"/chapter/advance-selector/","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Selector Kombinasi","anchor":"#selector-kombinasi"},{"depth":2,"value":"Multi Selector","anchor":"#multi-selector"},{"depth":2,"value":"Nested Selector","anchor":"#nested-selector"},{"depth":2,"value":"Interaction","anchor":"#interaction"},{"depth":2,"value":"Transition","anchor":"#transition"},{"depth":2,"value":"Input Interaction","anchor":"#input-interaction"},{"depth":2,"value":"Select By Attribute","anchor":"#select-by-attribute"}]}},{"node":{"title":"Layouting","path":"/chapter/layouting/","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Behaviour Default Dari Flex","anchor":"#behaviour-default-dari-flex"},{"depth":2,"value":"Auto Width","anchor":"#auto-width"},{"depth":2,"value":"Flex Wrap","anchor":"#flex-wrap"},{"depth":2,"value":"Flex Direction","anchor":"#flex-direction"},{"depth":2,"value":"Align Items","anchor":"#align-items"},{"depth":2,"value":"Justify Content","anchor":"#justify-content"}]}},{"node":{"title":"Praktik Layouting","path":"/chapter/praktik-layouting/","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Flex Container dan Flex Content","anchor":"#flex-container-dan-flex-content"},{"depth":2,"value":"Flex: 1;","anchor":"#flex-1"},{"depth":2,"value":"Nested Flexbox","anchor":"#nested-flexbox"},{"depth":2,"value":"Variasi Style","anchor":"#variasi-style"}]}},{"node":{"title":"Responsive","path":"/chapter/responsive/","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Berkenalan Dengan Viewport","anchor":"#berkenalan-dengan-viewport"},{"depth":2,"value":"Ukuran Viewport","anchor":"#ukuran-viewport"},{"depth":2,"value":"Basic Responsive","anchor":"#basic-responsive"},{"depth":2,"value":"Responsiveness Testing","anchor":"#responsiveness-testing"},{"depth":2,"value":"Aturan Responsive","anchor":"#aturan-responsive"}]}},{"node":{"title":"Menggunakan Framework","path":"/chapter/menggunakan-framework/","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Apa Itu Framework","anchor":"#apa-itu-framework"},{"depth":2,"value":"Membuat Framework","anchor":"#membuat-framework"},{"depth":2,"value":"Menginstall Framework","anchor":"#menginstall-framework"},{"depth":2,"value":"Menggunakan Class Framework","anchor":"#menggunakan-class-framework"},{"depth":2,"value":"Menggunakan Component Framework","anchor":"#menggunakan-component-framework"},{"depth":2,"value":"Memodifikasi Framework","anchor":"#memodifikasi-framework"},{"depth":2,"value":"Best Practice Editing","anchor":"#best-practice-editing"},{"depth":2,"value":"Mencari Target Class","anchor":"#mencari-target-class"},{"depth":2,"value":"Penutup","anchor":"#penutup"},{"depth":2,"value":"Credits","anchor":"#credits"}]}}]},"content":{"title":"Konsep Box","path":"/chapter/konsep-box/","content":"<h2 id=\"berkenalan-dengan-div\"><a href=\"#berkenalan-dengan-div\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Berkenalan Dengan <code>&#x3C;div></code></h2>\n<p><code>&#x3C;div></code> Merupakan element netral yang menjadi andalan para <em>frontend developer</em>. Kenapa? karena div ini mudah untuk distyling dan memiliki behaviour yang mudah diprediksi. Maksudnya gimana? hmm.. agak teknis sih. tapi untuk saat ini, mari kita sederhanakan. Intinya: <code>&#x3C;div></code> adalah <em>element</em> netral yang bisa kita gunakan untuk <em>styling</em>.</p>\n<p>Maksudnya netral adalah, <code>&#x3C;div></code> ini tidak berpengaruh pada SEO. Selain itu, dia tidak memiliki default styling yang rumit seperti misalnya <code>&#x3C;h1></code> mempunyai default styling yaitu <code>font-size</code> nya besar. Kalau <code>&#x3C;div></code> enggak, dia netral. Mangkannya lebih mudah untuk distyling.</p>\n<h2 id=\"membentuk-paradigma\"><a href=\"#membentuk-paradigma\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Membentuk Paradigma</h2>\n<p>Membentuk paradigma tentu bukanlah suatu hal yang mudah, tapi saya akan ceritakan bagaimana paradigma saya saat melakukan styling CSS—Khususnya saat menggunakan <code>&#x3C;div></code>.</p>\n<p>Jadi saya selalu membayangkan bahwa <code>&#x3C;div></code> adalah sebuah kotak berbentuk 2D yang bisa diwarnai, diberi ukuran, diberi jarak, dan diberi konten didalamnya. kotak 2D ini bisa dihiasi juga dengan shadow, bisa juga dipotong hingga berbentuk segitiga, lingkaran, oval, dll.</p>\n<p>Hanya saja defaultnya kotak 2D ini tidak memiliki garis, tidak memiliki ukuran. saking kecilnya—jika tidak diberi ukuran—maka saat kita hanya menuliskan </p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">black</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>tidak akan tampil apapun di browser. yaa karena div ini belum diapa-apain. Berbeda jika kita mulai memberinya ukuran misal:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n    <span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">black</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token unit\">px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token unit\">px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>maka muncul seperti gambar di bawah ini:</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 320 175' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-3954d26845ffb6002a290f03b8cd9422'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-3954d26845ffb6002a290f03b8cd9422)' width='320' height='175' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAjCAYAAAAkCQwqAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAA/klEQVRo3u3ZOwqFMBAF0KiFnx3Y%2bCvUdbj/Xhu1cA8Koo5MIA/sE9%2bAN3CTLpkcUmUUfXwonq7rovM86TgOvboMn2XOFAHwj0KkXP7xAsZxpL7vaRgGp9n3XdYL4ImfZtM0pJSiJEkoiiLrCcOQ4jimeZ7JnCkKIMsyDeA60zTJBCjLUhfo%2b771S3ue99tbLEBRFI9iXYT3BgAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAgA6CqKl1kEAS6UJvhz1BeeW%2bxAGmavvItzg0YcQDcpem6jvI8p7Ztqa5rq%2bGmi1mXZZEJsG0brevqPObiaI5Ka46%2bGXHN0S%2bPzwPc94n36BdH7EwAAAAASUVORK5CYII=' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"320\" alt=\"div saat diberi ukuran\" data-srcset=\"/css-itu-mudah/assets/static/black-box.b82b75d.430ebee5e4ce0e8f57bec46684543fce.png 320w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-src=\"/css-itu-mudah/assets/static/black-box.b82b75d.430ebee5e4ce0e8f57bec46684543fce.png\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/css-itu-mudah/assets/static/black-box.b82b75d.430ebee5e4ce0e8f57bec46684543fce.png\" width=\"320\" alt=\"div saat diberi ukuran\"></noscript></p>\n<h2 id=\"mengenal-paddding\"><a href=\"#mengenal-paddding\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Mengenal Paddding</h2>\n<p>Atau jika kita tidak ingin memberi ukuran secara spesifik atau mengikuti ukuran konten yang ada didalamnya, maka bisa ditambahkan text dan padding seperti berikut:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n    <span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">black</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">white</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token unit\">px</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token unit\">px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ukuranku Fleksibel Lho. Tergantung Teksnya<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 895 147' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-cb645ebb5c0bd404f4a22789cd9f3b83'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-cb645ebb5c0bd404f4a22789cd9f3b83)' width='895' height='147' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAALCAYAAADP9otxAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAABQUlEQVRIx%2bWW7YqCQBSGzSLIXNZ1oSI207QPcy2zMmujrWCvpG68C4lntcVw%2b/gvOPAw57znvOfHMAwjkPMlHI9HYg6Hw4UkTvR0ntZv%2bx9x25tFhGiRa0ql0sNCsVhEFMU7Pe4XC4VrHPc9G14ul%2b%2b0QuSNfVlBCNcbgskI59MlCFfst2tM08R2xux2G5ZhyGw2ZbP5Zr5YYPe7%2bP6UoW2jqirL1QrXjbxRLZj5jL1JpH0x6HUZDEf87Ld4Ex/f87Bth3dVydYNqDca6G0NXdfpDWws00DTNBTljWazSccwLrVYa0f7m6Lw0WqhRVQqFWq1Or1%2bn/k8wOzotLQ2jjvCdYZUJJmuZV58lmVhGB2U15frTcjIIeT8DahWq8iyTLInccJt/pSUN%2b35i//PkCQpMwin04k8I%2bT%2bI3Q%2bn8kzv6q3EaEaQnaIAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"895\" alt=\"Basic padding div\" data-srcset=\"/css-itu-mudah/assets/static/basic-padding.82a2fbd.90588cd3c4aa4cf05488e82ca9aa1a83.png 480w, /css-itu-mudah/assets/static/basic-padding.49ab861.90588cd3c4aa4cf05488e82ca9aa1a83.png 895w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 895px) 100vw, 895px\" data-src=\"/css-itu-mudah/assets/static/basic-padding.49ab861.90588cd3c4aa4cf05488e82ca9aa1a83.png\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/css-itu-mudah/assets/static/basic-padding.49ab861.90588cd3c4aa4cf05488e82ca9aa1a83.png\" width=\"895\" alt=\"Basic padding div\"></noscript></p>\n<h2 id=\"mengenal-margin\"><a href=\"#mengenal-margin\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Mengenal Margin</h2>\n<p>Selain bisa memberinya ukuran, kita juga bisa memberinya jarak menggunakan <code>margin</code>.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n    <span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">black</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\">white</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token unit\">px</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token unit\">px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">margin-bottom</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token unit\">px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Ukuranku Fleksibel Lho. Tergantung Teksnya<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Aku Div Ke 2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 817 301' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-8bbd38a666b048a7d15aee0c5c0bf021'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-8bbd38a666b048a7d15aee0c5c0bf021)' width='817' height='301' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAYCAYAAABKtPtEAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAB10lEQVRYw%2b2WfWvaUBTGEzVJU9C2qTFp82LUaIxuqau58WWdM23ZHGMbYx9Ewe/mhxPh2b3iRveHo2xjgjcXfiTclwfO5ZxzHwGcD2G5XIJnBDrANfl8fu%2biKIrPWvudBiOXE/fM51AoFA6KoCgKOlEPYbMO0zRh2S663RA1z8X5uYbebR8vuwEaDR/Npo9O5wXqvg/PdbZz11fXUE9PEUURLMui2Ki6LrxqFbbroepY0C4ruLmJ0A3bsG0HDt1nmFdQT5TDZ4AsywhoUKR/i4QQjN9M8fCQYkD68P0WGs0Ar0cDJIMhRkOCwXCMmMRwHRu93iuQOMZZqYSgH